{"tid":615452,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"［畫畫JJ] 每日練功團","createTime":"2018-04-03T11:24:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T05:09:07.000Z","uid":34781,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c105e07fe62291c394c3733ec1625a5a7ed7bb0a","tid":615452,"uid":34781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T11:24:03.000Z","msg":"打算開一個畫畫練功團，新手老手都歡迎<br />\n<br />\n目的係可以有一班同伴互相督促提點，然後一齊進步<br />\n<br />\n最基本活動係每日要po畫 (唔使完整作品，塗鴉/練習/進度都ok) 最緊要係每日都要動手畫野<br />\n<br />\n暫時希望可以有20人先 (已有7,8位巴絲join左)<br />\n<br />\n齊人之後會問大家拎少少資料 (例如畫齡，畫開d咩等等) 之後會跟資料分組，3-5人一組，盡量希望每組會有一個經驗多d既帶住<br />\n<br />\n之後每組都會有一個組長，最主要都係搞下定期活動咁(例如每月主題畫咁樣)<br />\n<br />\n有興趣巴絲可以留低tg"},{"pid":"522656cf0e06b7ba456d3ab8c83ff09c3a41be34","tid":615452,"uid":176143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T11:45:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/popopo852\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpopopo852&d=mwDQPt1y6DjBgKsiltFnrjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=d795a8a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/popopo852</a>"},{"pid":"4357c834ee60dbf0476a6e4064bef7aecaa4d9cc","tid":615452,"uid":69359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T12:13:30.000Z","msg":"熱烈支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d7433b98a6c4c4956834da59ba35bc2b64c5bd","tid":615452,"uid":171838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T12:59:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://T.me/maomaomeow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FT.me%2Fmaomaomeow&d=mwDQPt1y6DjBgKsiltFnrjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=548de9e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">T.me/maomaomeow</a>"},{"pid":"250e4204605bcde80837698d4576710e1c0a0025","tid":615452,"uid":14826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T15:33:12.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"4e6db02e629e3c7b3f20bbdff5665c68bb4a9f9e","tid":615452,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl